  <entry>
    <title>日本行脚（六）</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2024/02/25/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%A1%8C%E8%84%9A%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AD%EF%BC%89/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2024/02/25/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%A1%8C%E8%84%9A%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AD%EF%BC%89/</id>
    <published>2024-02-25T10:10:26.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-11-21T14:33:06.272Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Day6行程：东京大学一日游，告别霓虹"><a href="#Day6行程：东京大学一日游，告别霓虹" class="headerlink" title="Day6行程：东京大学一日游，告别霓虹"></a>Day6行程：东京大学一日游，告别霓虹</h1><p>最后一天，下午4点出发去机场，早上没有行程，导游让我们自行安排。于是毅然决定去我心心念念的高校—东京大学。</p><p>早上八点起床，在酒店吃完早餐，就按照导游提供的路线，出发去坐地铁。大概碰巧遇上了上班早高峰，见识了一波东京的“人潮汹涌”。</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/f3a6bdc9272b41c11e21f2eecebb763.jpg"></p><p>大约坐了半个小时，到达东京大学附近：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ca11bdc246550471282c25f99fbe9e6.jpg"></p><p>到达东京大学赤门（但据说最近几年都不开了，所以只能从旁边的另一个门进去）：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/00e423375b5e794cf63e3eda8b3219b.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/848125080b5eb9f89db8495342b7955.jpg"></p><p>成功踏入日本top1大学！！！</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ecee3c5b2aa2970f3f4f30fa2c83bfb.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/e7a742800bbc6ad7251778dbe5104a5.jpg"></p><p>生物科学专攻：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/147336189943af9a0c43634fd5a0ea8.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/9b66f0186f5070e3e3678b2a62bef7d.jpg"></p><p>博物馆（很可惜当天闭馆，没能进去看看）：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/7f50433d89c0a35156da560fb76d622.jpg"></p><p>医学部&amp;医学部附属医院：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/3b6a82c763fa3a230fea6b898575f64.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/90750b5d232762cad9ae40f8795f127.jpg"></p><p>东大操场&amp;周围场馆&amp;自然景观：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/22d3506d415b2a508da4a894c026bd4.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/7b2999c4b4544df6f4b6acd39c2f921.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/8635534cd0e9a172fe8b3449bd06b17.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/0295ab69706b0edfd01f362205f9f45.png"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/3c3d86942e7a7e8172abaaa4d1abde3.jpg"></p><p>社会科学研究所：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2a06fe7fc7544e8ca2ecf018bbed1db.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/302da1013378562972793964945fd9c.jpg"></p><p>情报学府：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/77b6a984f754d483235866189b9aeb8.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/a50c310ac2a2d311428589d440b3ca9.jpg"></p><p>东大综合图书馆（因为那段时间是学生的考试周，图书馆不允许校外人员进入，有点可惜）：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ccf9c8ef2add2bad55b596762ba0b78.jpg"></p><p>跟想象中差异比较大的是，东大内部的大部分建筑都是西式，只有极小部分是日式的建筑风格。</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/3a5c9f3db44f8b1de7b7c3e2318778a.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/fbf47313e878066aa513814777b112d.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2a7b7d9a68cf774f1007bd19bcda9c4.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/a9b9be7606d99b679e65659a126875e.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/e54bbd02785b429a8833f0d4b227dd7.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/4f21bb687113d988df8c398ccb5cee8.jpg"></p><p>雕像集合：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/f05d16288963129a46bd8ddd6c01567.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/b3b08d7b1884c1b2197ba98e98afa3f.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/7b0c5675f7955a44a44731992ab5ecf.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/4a905e7002031197c31d9fd09b6f167.jpg"></p><p>东京大学理学系直通车！</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/bc4e99f9cf8d529ec773af69a4d5c9b.jpg"></p><p>理学部场馆：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/e7150878c739990427a61adad8cc82e.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2fee96a82c8b021da58c50de0a10e0a.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/b19390097ab6b597bc10856c17e2d04.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/8352702440289986eba1bd952be6fad.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/37ae1d4e57c04de3a34793eb44ab736.jpg"></p><p>理学部某展览馆：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/57c3ea4c621ef33feb61cc1b74b0285.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/0d63aa2fe47930494eba2757350ae31.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/7ed9ad86967005ae08a10655b7f9489.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/9997505259d0bf4aafea35b8e780e59.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/4cd3810ed7fb0af529e635b1d84b2e9.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/541b49fefdf76b91855eb980e125768.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/9410b4d8cbda89d887ae49d19fe2499.jpg"></p><p>浅浅打个卡叭~</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/3e2f73aec486da69b81b9141fc28604.jpg"></p><p>转战工学部：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/a6d12c43a34a2384b91a7bbe2db66ba.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/94de39fa85f62441913061a6d1ff6bf.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/b3258f3f10e467962cc8b5245fdacee.png"></p><p>打卡东京大学安田讲堂~</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/f348ab970bbf06e91319fc32350f718.jpg"></p><p>在中央食堂（安田讲堂的地下层）浅浅吃个中饭~（东大的食堂价格比外面的餐厅便宜一点…）</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/63bde1ddad63fe9739e4b009645feea.jpg"></p><p>打卡东京大学铁门：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/446e77a6533b8c2e5d73cefa221e70e.png"></p><p>药学部：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/873ca2b4bfb5e84f638e0f813dfeec3.jpg"></p><p>地震研究所（这么玩是吧，好好好）：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/e0ce65548b60a7eeadf98f639aaad25.jpg"></p><p>出校后，在东大附近闲逛，感觉建筑风格明显由西式转为了日式…</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/3269b170cd03441287c6d3a63406f46.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/688a2c0a44ecfee46edc59b54982c72.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/54658aab4f54065d9c2d4c69baacad1.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/dde6ee69e554bba58092e6a6a005f21.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/a6c57493a9cc577b5a527462773358b.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/39fe10cb7a2317629ba8f3ed5301e6e.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/e19788273c9e7fd6c8c40807ff2d2c2.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/9fb39123d6e3f89c99a02639cebc53b.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/ecdf5d418154f37b86e10d6826f119d.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/1bee40267381bd973169f326d6f7c32.jpg"></p><p>西式—日式—现代化街道：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/85959d96dc09dbf5211d8338738d598.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/592a98e0dc4f12e1e83eff21d30227d.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/68d187ff76b92bc43af7c1b5e3c2dbf.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/1d15ef5a7b9b35d92a5387575e390ca.jpg"></p><p>下午2:30，启程回酒店，告别东大！</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/52b6ca0451c3d08e735acb91eff850b.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/be7ba9d1efd38810ef31929c4162c9d.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/3d5966d615c43bc709cec57d671ade0.jpg"></p><p>回到酒店大约3:30，人到齐后，出发去东京成田机场，花了三个多小时飞到萧山，结束为期六天的日本之行！</p><p>日本、縁があって再会！</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/33e8d497d27126e4543f1542755ea46.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/3129eb1fc3212e849c75fd9b06f6de2.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/9d9d95d2f46c01b1cf816f92bb55dc2.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/03e681216707f70bbea36b76404a9ba.jpg"></p>]]></content>
    
    
