  <entry>
    <title>日本行脚（五）</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2024/02/25/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%A1%8C%E8%84%9A%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2024/02/25/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%A1%8C%E8%84%9A%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89/</id>
    <published>2024-02-25T04:57:29.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-11-21T14:33:06.291Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Day5行程：鹤岗八幡宫×镰仓大佛×镰仓高校×台场"><a href="#Day5行程：鹤岗八幡宫×镰仓大佛×镰仓高校×台场" class="headerlink" title="Day5行程：鹤岗八幡宫×镰仓大佛×镰仓高校×台场"></a>Day5行程：鹤岗八幡宫×镰仓大佛×镰仓高校×台场</h1><h2 id="1、鹤岗八幡宫"><a href="#1、鹤岗八幡宫" class="headerlink" title="1、鹤岗八幡宫"></a>1、鹤岗八幡宫</h2><p>位于日本神奈川县镰仓市的神社，是三大八幡宫之一。</p><p>鸟居：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/cc8ee5401151d8def3ef04ba818e289.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/eb515bc26e7a6a21a922cf8d8d3d39d.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2afbeba37500ecb80227ea5d829084c.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/804c788f1ee96677b24fe34291f2e2b.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/f38853436698b00d549d6ff7eb82581.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/99209de6b4b117ea7e39be583b4ce7e.jpg"></p><p>从鹤岗八幡宫出来，坐电车去看镰仓大佛。</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/675d8a343842611d639d377df32db99.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/bb5e0e2485a1d604840f2876d3642f1.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/feec3dfd630935daa119a39bd32d712.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/5f8bae23f91617f8a1a588835d763e7.jpg"></p><mark class="hl-label default">注：日本的电车不像国内的地铁一样便宜，坐一次大约要两三百日元。</mark> <h2 id="2、镰仓大佛"><a href="#2、镰仓大佛" class="headerlink" title="2、镰仓大佛"></a>2、镰仓大佛</h2><p>位于古都镰仓的净土宗寺院高德院内，是古都镰仓的象征。</p><p>镰仓大佛的门票是张书签，能带回去留作纪念~</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/a69d390c65ae9d5a6f7ffbfcb4b8cff.jpg"></p><p>入口处的洗手池：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/7cbd05d58c4d87fffb46a7024f4168e.jpg"></p><p>不是，哥们儿，你板着个脸给谁看呢…</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/a3fd3d749d7d2558573ef2df03c936b.jpg"></p><p>长达1.8米的草鞋。这双草鞋最初在 1951 年由一群孩子编织，他们希望佛陀能够穿上草鞋，走过日本每一寸土地。</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/d7da4d115223566a44516c95eb5a9dd.jpg"></p><p>佛像两侧的木屋与石碑：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/a0188ff132af4fb988fe49a5396803b.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/c548c46711b683ea44ed77373589c48.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2e9c430ec35d15f8e287af1065ce409.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/f8e47d2b5a2ac24390f5bb06c2d949f.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/599055b76b58eb2e6187bfa5d352827.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/b0f2c06fed588c15382e111d1a3b943.jpg"></p><h2 id="3、镰仓高校"><a href="#3、镰仓高校" class="headerlink" title="3、镰仓高校"></a>3、镰仓高校</h2><p>镰仓高校最有名的莫过于动漫《灌篮高手》的取景地。坐江之岛电铁，是游览镰仓的最佳方式。</p><p>面朝大海，春暖花开~</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/dcabf3184e67382d67c9c8e107ee32e.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/eaffba456107e99b6d50b8e74240188.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/2b6c3accbaf48b36ed1b4f2793517d1.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/d938cd8e9051247cebd94be5bf90ee9.jpg"></p><p>网红打卡点—《灌篮高手》取景地</p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/899507280bebb8d9d540709560e0dde.jpg" style="zoom:150%;" /><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/5fc77758055a4d784ca28b242e594f9.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/3d7e2f3709d30253b7337abfe4ce110.jpg"></p><p>镰仓高等学校：</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/cd0be4dc01804ae10ad47cd5440d5e2.jpg"></p><h2 id="4、台场"><a href="#4、台场" class="headerlink" title="4、台场"></a>4、台场</h2><p>东京市中心唯一的海滩，也是东京奥运会的主题地。</p><p>东京自由女神像…噂嘟假嘟？（毁谤啊！我告你毁谤啊！！！）</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/fc361673ae191c6501a1b2048a832be.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/70a8cb5b1cd0a9bebb9612b86a1fccb.jpg"></p><p>“一柱擎天”</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/3d882cf300e2bf8c28de1eee5366fd6.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/9f31cea070b75439315962978174d66.jpg"></p><p>居然还有高达？！</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/b6ae022182d6e9d74ee8dfb25b2d971.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/8b55c408c3445d3309ff11ac278f468.jpg"></p><h2 id="番外"><a href="#番外" class="headerlink" title="番外"></a>番外</h2><p>“你相信光吗？”</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/5066bafb4a9c8c63e2540358fc7e09b.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/8e78952088ca773ebad21fcaf9db52c.jpg"></p><h2 id="番外2"><a href="#番外2" class="headerlink" title="番外2"></a>番外2</h2><p>浅吃一下晚饭~</p><p><img src="https://qtdsswk.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/f24326eb4d071b449d23e787847b614.jpg"></p>]]></content>
    
    
